import java.nio.charset.Charset

paragraphs.text:
case class StrucSummary(
    v_structure_summary_ref_id: String , 
    pdb_id: String,
    structure_title: String, 
    experimentalTechnique: String, 
    ndb_id: String,
    resolution: Float,
    release_date: String,
    deposition_date: String,
    revision_date: String,
    molecular_weight: Float,
    macromolecule_type: String,
    residue_count: Integer,
    atom_site_count: Integer,
    pdb_doi: String
    
)

val ssummary = structText.map(s => s.split(";")).filter(s => s(9) != null).filter(s => s(11) != null).map(
    s => StrucSummary(
            s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
            s(1).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(3).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(4).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(5).replaceAll("\"", "").toFloat,
            s(6).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(7).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
            s(8).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(9).replaceAll("\"", "").toFloat,        
            s(10).replaceAll("\"", ""),
            s(11).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt,
            s(12).replaceAll("\"", "").toInt,
            s(13).replaceAll("\"", "")
        )
).toDF()
ssummary.registerTempTable("ssummary")
